This chrome extension provides some additional tweaks and options not availible on the original site.

Features:

* Subject in comments
* Custom font in the comments
* Custom comment size
* Ability to delete the draft in the old version of "Create new post" page
* Ability to disable gradients on comments on the comments page
* Always show comment controls

The source: https://github.com/can3p/ljcustomize

Pull requests with new features, fixes and translations are always welcome!
